### 1. Optimisation des Meta Tags
Fournis des recommandations concrètes:

```vue
<script setup>
import { useHead } from '@unhead/vue'

useHead({
  title: 'Titre optimisé | Marque',
  meta: [
    { name: 'description', content: 'Description optimisée 150-160 caractères' },
    { property: 'og:title', content: 'Titre pour reseaux sociaux' },
    { property: 'og:description', content: 'Description Open Graph' },
    { property: 'og:image', content: 'https://example.com/og-image.jpg' },
    { name: 'twitter:card', content: 'summary_large_image' }
  ]
})
</script>
```

